es, 1981-1982\n* Mandy Owen, 1983-1984\n* Mike Smith, 1984-1985\n* Charles Payne, 1987-1988\n* Malcolm Cockburn, Gerald Guenther, 1988-1989\n* Malcolm Cockburn, 1990-1991\n* David Landew, 1991-1993\n* Will Trevor, 1993-1994\n* Derek Morgan, 1994-1995\n* Tracy Slawson, 2000-2001\n* Jeremy Blackburn, 2001-2002 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://uk.linkedin.com/in/jeremy-blackburn-5033763b|title=Jeremy Blackburn|website=uk.linkedin.com/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n* James Rogers, 2002-2003 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://henryjacksonsociety.org/staff/james-rogers/|title=JAMES ROGERS|website=henryjacksonsociety.org/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n* Paul Hagan, 2003-2004 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://be.linkedin.com/in/paul-hagan-74729151|title=Paul Hagan|website=uk.linkedin.com/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n* David McElhill, 2004-2005\n* Sam Garbett, 2009-2010\n* Eilif Swensen, 2010-2011\n* Yvonne K. Rinkart, 2011-2012 <ref>{{cite journal |last=Rinkaer |first=Y. K. |date=2011 |title=Interstate |journal=Interstate |volume=92 |pages=2|ISSN=20516932}}</ref>\n* Alex Serafimov, 2012-2013\n* Alex Middleton, 2013-2014\n* Akos Erzse, 2014-2015\n* Alexandra Hird, 2015-2016\n* Tirion Kerr, 2016-2017\n* Ben Brotherwood, 2017-2018\n* Agata Kusiak, 2018-2019\n* Ellis Drewe Jones-Thurling, 2019- <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.linkedin.com/in/ellis-jones-thurling-968a31145/|title=Ellis Jones-Thurling|website=uk.linkedin.com/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>}}\n\n== Deputy Editor-in-Chiefs ==\nThe following persons have been [[Deputy Editor-in-Chief]] of the journal:\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Nathan Anderson, 2019-<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abersu.co.uk/society/ips/|title=INTERNATIONAL POLITICS SOCIETY|website=www.abersu.co.uk/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>}}\n\n== Welsh Language Editors ==\nThe following persons have been Welsh [[Language Editor]] of the journal:\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Dylan Lewis-Rowlands, 2019- <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abersu.co.uk/society/ips/|title=INTERNATIONAL POLITICS SOCIETY|website=www.abersu.co.uk/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>}}\n\n== Managing Editor ==\nThe following persons have been [[Managing Editor]] of the journal:\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Johannes Lindem, 2019-<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abersu.co.uk/news/article/umabersu/AUTUMN-VOLUNTEER-OFFICER-BY-ELECTIONS-AND-ACADEMIC-REP-ELECTION-RESULTS/|title=AUTUMN VOLUNTEER OFFICER BY-ELECTIONS AND ACADEMIC REP ELECTION RESULTS|website=www.abersu.co.uk/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>}}\n\n== Treasurers ==\nThe following persons have been [[Treasurer]] of the journal:\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Richard Hodgetts, 2019-}}\n\n== Secretaries ==\nThe following persons have been [[Secretary]] of the journal:\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Harry Young, 2019-}}\n\n== Substantive Editors ==\nThe following persons have been [[Substantive Editor]] of the journal: <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.geoff-hart.com/articles/2000/substantive.htm|title=What is substantive editing?|website=www.geoff-hart.com/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Liberty Elliot, 2019-}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|https://interstate1965.wixsite.com/website}}\n* [http://www.inquiriesjournal.com/journals/10/interstate--journal-of-international-affairs Online archives]\n\n[[Category:Publications established in 1965]]\n[[Category:Academic journals edited by students]]\n[[Category:International relations journals]]\n[[Category:Triannual journals]]\n", "text_old": "<!-- Please do not remove or change this AfD message until the discussion has been closed. -->\n{{Article for deletion/dated|page=Interstate Journal of Politics and International Relations|timestamp=20200402184949|year=2020|month=April|day=2|substed=yes|help=off}}\n<!-- Once discussion is closed, please place on talk page: {{Old AfD multi|page=Interstate Journal of Politics and International Relations|date=2 April 2020|result='''keep'''}} -->\n<!-- End of AfD message, feel free to edit beyond this point -->\n\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:Interstate Journal of Politics and International Relations.}}\n{{multiple issues|\n{{notability|date=August 2015}}\n{{one source|date=August 2015}}\n{{third-party|date=August 2015}}\n}}\n{{Infobox journal\n| title = Interstate Journal of Politics and International Relations\n| image = \n| caption = \n| former_names = State, Interstate - Journal of Political Affairs, Aberystwyth Journal of World Affairs\n| discipline = [[International relations]]\n| language = English, [[Welsh language|Welsh]]\n| abbreviation = Interstate J. Int. Aff.\n| editor = \n| publisher = Department of International Politics, Aberystwyth University\n| country = United Kingdom\n| history = 1965-present\n| frequency = Triannual\n| openaccess = Yes\n| license = \n| impact = \n| impact-year = \n| ISSN = 2051-6932\n| eISSN = \n| CODEN = \n| JSTOR = \n| LCCN = \n| OCLC = 7830152\n| website = https://interstate1965.wixsite.com/website\n| link1 = https://www.aber.ac.uk/en/interpol/current-students/undergraduate/interstate/\n| link1-name = Journal page on University Website\n| link2 = https://interstate1965.wixsite.com/website/file-share\n| link2-name = Online tables of contents\n| link3 = http://www.studentpulse.com/journals/10/interstate--journal-of-international-affairs\n| link3-name = Online archives\n}}\nThe '''''Interstate Journal of Politics and International Relations''''' is a triannual [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] produced by undergraduates and postgraduates from the Department of International Politics at [[Aberystwyth University]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aber.ac.uk/en/interpol/supporting-you/undergraduate/interstate/|title=Interstate - Department of International Politics, Aberystwyth University|website=www.aber.ac.uk|language=en|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n\n== Editor-in-Chiefs ==\nThe following persons have been [[Editor-in-Chief]] of the journal:<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.inquiriesjournal.com/journals/10/interstate--journal-of-international-affairs|title=Interstate - Journal of International Affairs - JournalQuest|website=www.inquiriesjournal.com|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* J. Lynton Jones, 1965-1966 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aber.ac.uk/en/development/alumniprofiles/alumprofiles/lyntonjones/|title=Lynton Jones|website=www.aber.ac.uk/en/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n* Andrew Guy, 1967-1968 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aber.ac.uk/en/development/alumniprofiles/alumprofiles/andrewguy/|title=Andrew Guy|website=www.aber.ac.uk/en/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n* [[Michael MccGwire]], 1968-1969 <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/obituaries/2016/05/19/commander-michael-mccgwire--obituary/|title=Commander Michael MccGwire \u2013 obituary|date=2016-05-19|work=The Telegraph|access-date=2020-04-02|language=en-GB|issn=0307-1235}}</ref>\n* [[Michael Clarke (academic)|Michael Clarke]], Ian Hopwood, 1969-1970\n* Anne Marek, 1970-1971\n* [[Michael Clarke (academic)|Michael Clarke]], 1971-1972\n* [[Michael Clarke (academic)|Michael Clarke]], Anne Marek, Ian Palmer, 1972-73\n* Richard Comotto, 1974-1975 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.reading.ac.uk/search/search-staff-details.aspx?id=10324|title=RICHARD COMOTTO|website=www.reading.ac.uk/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n* William Bebb, 1975-1976\n* Jim Evans, 1976-1977\n* Tom Evans, 1977-1978\n* Guy Kitching, Ian McMahon, 1978-1979\n* Gregory Luton, 1979-1980\n* Sam Pease, 1980-1981\n* David Knowles, 1981-1982\n* Mandy Owen, 1983-1984\n* Mike Smith, 1984-1985\n* Charles Payne, 1987-1988\n* Malcolm Cockburn, Gerald Guenther, 1988-1989\n* Malcolm Cockburn, 1990-1991\n* David Landew, 1991-1993\n* Will Trevor, 1993-1994\n* Derek Morgan, 1994-1995\n* Tracy Slawson, 2000-2001\n* Jeremy Blackburn, 2001-2002 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://uk.linkedin.com/in/jeremy-blackburn-5033763b|title=Jeremy Blackburn|website=uk.linkedin.com/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n* James Rogers, 2002-2003 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://henryjacksonsociety.org/staff/james-rogers/|title=JAMES ROGERS|website=henryjacksonsociety.org/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n* Paul Hagan, 2003-2004 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://be.linkedin.com/in/paul-hagan-74729151|title=Paul Hagan|website=uk.linkedin.com/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n* David McElhill, 2004-2005\n* Sam Garbett, 2009-2010\n* Eilif Swensen, 2010-2011\n* Yvonne K. Rinkart, 2011-2012 <ref>{{cite journal |last=Rinkaer |first=Y. K. |date=2011 |title=Interstate |journal=Interstate |volume=92 |pages=2|ISSN=20516932}}</ref>\n* Alex Serafimov, 2012-2013\n* Alex Middleton, 2013-2014\n* Akos Erzse, 2014-2015\n* Alexandra Hird, 2015-2016\n* Tirion Kerr, 2016-2017\n* Ben Brotherwood, 2017-2018\n* Agata Kusiak, 2018-2019\n* Ellis Drewe Jones-Thurling, 2019- <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.linkedin.com/in/ellis-jones-thurling-968a31145/|title=Ellis Jones-Thurling|website=uk.linkedin.com/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>}}\n\n== Deputy Editor-in-Chiefs ==\nThe following persons have been [[Deputy Editor-in-Chief]] of the journal:\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Nathan Anderson, 2019-<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abersu.co.uk/society/ips/|title=INTERNATIONAL POLITICS SOCIETY|website=www.abersu.co.uk/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>}}\n\n== Welsh Language Editors ==\nThe following persons have been Welsh [[Language Editor]] of the journal:\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Dylan Lewis-Rowlands, 2019- <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abersu.co.uk/society/ips/|title=INTERNATIONAL POLITICS SOCIETY|website=www.abersu.co.uk/|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>}}\n\n== Managing Editor ==\nThe following persons have been [[Managing Editor]] of the journal:\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Johannes Lindem, 2019-<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abersu.co.uk/news/article/umabersu/AUTUMN-VOLUNTEER-OFFICER-BY-ELECTIONS-AND-ACADEMIC-REP-ELECTION-RESULTS/|title=AUTUMN VOLUNTEER OFFICER BY-ELECTIONS AND ACADEMIC REP ELECTION RESULTS|websi